# CloudQA Form Automation Test

## Project Overview
Automated testing solution for CloudQA practice form using C# and Selenium WebDriver.

## Features
- Robust Element Location: Multiple locator strategies per field
- Self-Healing Tests: Adapts when HTML structure changes
- Comprehensive Reporting: Detailed test execution logs
- Error Handling: Graceful failure handling with informative messages

## Test Coverage
1. Name Field Testing - Text input validation
2. Email Field Testing - Email format and input validation  
3. Phone Field Testing - Numeric input validation

## Setup Instructions
1. Install Visual Studio 2022
2. Install Chrome browser
3. Download ChromeDriver and add to PATH
4. Clone/download this project
5. Run: `dotnet restore` (if needed)
6. Execute: `dotnet run` or press F5 in Visual Studio

## Test Strategy
- Uses 8+ different locator strategies per field
- Falls back gracefully when primary locators fail
- Provides detailed logging for debugging
- Validates actual vs expected field values

## Results
- Test execution summary with pass/fail counts
- Individual field test results
- Performance and reliability metrics
